<< /DA (/CourierStd 10.00 Tf 0 g) /F 4 /FT /Tx /Ff 8388608 /MK << >> /P 22 0 R /Parent 43 0 R /Q 1 /Rect [ 419.086 107.357 557.416 127.607 ] /StructParent 19 /Subtype /Widget /T <feff004500610072006e0069006e006700730034005f004400650063005b0030005d> /TU (Yearly Income) /Type /Annot >>
